<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Dom Barrera | Systems That Work</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --panel: #111827;
      --card: #1f2937;
      --text: #f8fafc;
      --muted: #cbd5e1;
      --accent: #38bdf8;
      --accent-2: #22c55e;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0f172a 0%, #111827 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .wrap {
      max-width: 1060px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 20px 72px;
    }
    .hero {
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 36px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
    }
    .eyebrow {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.8vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
    }
    .sub {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 760px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .btn.primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #082f49;
      border-color: transparent;
    }
    .btn.secondary {
      color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 22px;
    }
    .metric {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--accent-2);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    h2 {
      margin: 44px 0 16px;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }
    ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .service-list li, .proof-list li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .tag-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .tag {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(56,189,248,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.2);
      color: #bae6fd;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 44px;
      padding: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    .small { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .hero { padding: 24px; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="eyebrow">Portfolio</div>
      <h1>Systems that help small businesses get customers and run better.</h1>
      <p class="sub">
        I’m Dom Barrera. I’ve spent 10+ years building real-world programs — from federal food systems to $110M campaigns. Now I help small businesses launch fast with websites, lead capture, and simple automation that actually works.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn primary" href="mailto:dom@rural-bites.com">Work with me</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/barreradb" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">View LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="metric">10+ Years</div>
        <div>Building programs, systems, and operations that work in the real world.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="metric">$110M+</div>
        <div>In long-term public funding supported through campaign and coalition work.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="metric">2.9M+</div>
        <div>Meals delivered through a statewide non-congregate food access program.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="metric">30,000+</div>
        <div>Children reached through large-scale service delivery systems in Colorado.</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <h2>What I can help with</h2>
    <section class="two-col">
      <div class="card">
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Simple websites built to help you get found and get calls</li>
          <li>Lead capture systems that turn visitors into real inquiries</li>
          <li>AI chat and auto-response setups for faster follow-up</li>
          <li>Landing pages for side hustles, service businesses, and local brands</li>
          <li>Fast launch support for people monetizing a skill, service, truck, land, or home-based business</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <strong>Best fit clients</strong>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">Local businesses</span>
          <span class="tag">Service providers</span>
          <span class="tag">Home-based businesses</span>
          <span class="tag">Side hustlers</span>
          <span class="tag">Founders</span>
          <span class="tag">Contractors</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <h2>Why clients trust me</h2>
    <section class="card">
      <ul class="proof-list">
        <li>I’ve launched programs from scratch, managed complex logistics, and built systems that hold up under pressure.</li>
        <li>I’ve managed $6M+ in budgets and worked across public, nonprofit, and civic tech environments.</li>
        <li>I focus on what actually moves the business: getting found, capturing leads, and making it easy for people to contact you.</li>
        <li>I don’t just build pages that look good. I build setups that are meant to produce results.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <h2>How I work</h2>
    <section class="two-col">
      <div class="card">
        <strong>1. Clarify the offer</strong>
        <p class="small">We get clear on what you sell, who it’s for, and what action you want people to take.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <strong>2. Build fast</strong>
        <p class="small">I turn that into a simple website, landing page, or lead system that is easy to use and easy to update.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <strong>3. Get you live</strong>
        <p class="small">The goal is speed, clarity, and something you can actually use right away.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <strong>4. Improve over time</strong>
        <p class="small">Once it’s live, you can keep refining the message, follow-up, and conversion flow.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="footer">
      <strong>Need a simple site or system that helps your business actually move?</strong><br />
      Email <a href="mailto:dom@rural-bites.com" style="color:#7dd3fc;">dom@rural-bites.com</a> or connect on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/barreradb" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" style="color:#7dd3fc;">LinkedIn</a>.
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
